<a href="../images/feb2019/Stateofclimate_Indices_tg90p_2019_month_nc__2019-02-16T00-00-00Z_large.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="../images/feb2019/Stateofclimate_Indices_tg90p_2019_month_nc__2019-02-16T00-00-00Z.png" ></a>
