<a href="../images/feb2019/Stateofclimate_Feb2019_tx_0_25deg_2019_month_pct_box_nc_baselayers_world_polygons_tx_box_baselayers_overlay_2019-02-16T00-00-00Z_large.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="../images/feb2019/Stateofclimate_Feb2019_tx_0_25deg_2019_month_pct_box_nc_baselayers_world_polygons_tx_box_baselayers_overlay_2019-02-16T00-00-00Z.png" ></a>
