<h3>Cloudiness and Radiation</h3>
<br><br>
The difference between Southwestern and Northeastern Europe can also be seen for cloudiness and radiation (Figure 16, 17): a very sunny southwestern area mainly influenced by high pressure, particularly in Spain and France, contrasted with much cloudiness and little sunshine / shortwave radiation over northwestern Russia due to frequently passing precipitation systems.
